William T. Kirby v. Louis Zlotnick Henry W. O’Brien, for the appellee (defendant). James F. Bingham, for the appellant (plaintiff). Henry W. O’Brien, on the motion. James F. Bingham, in opposition. Submitted April 28

decided June 3, 1969

Argued June 3 decided June 3, 1969

The supplemental motion by the defendant dated April 22, 1969, to dismiss the appeal from the Superior Court in Fairfield County at Stamford is denied.

The motion by the defendant to erase or strike the plaintiff’s request for a finding and draft finding in the appeal from the Superior Court in Fairfield County at Stamford is denied.
